<br>
Suddenly she puts the paper aside and turns to Llylewen and Nullo, who are playing cards near the now perpetually open Gnomish Murphy Bar. &quot;Sisters, I have an idea.&quot;<br>
<br>
Llylewen places her cards on the table and grins at Nullo. &quot;Queen's Court. Ha!&quot; <br>
<br>
Nullo calmly places her cards over Llylewen's. &quot;King's Cross,&quot; she replies with a benevolently sweet smile. &quot;I win. What was that, Mirabor?&quot;<br>
<br>
Mirabor chuckles. &quot;I'm no good at cards, but perhaps another game. Well, 'tis not a game so much as its a way ta get ta know each other better. Therefore I think some trivia is in order. Fer example, did ya know that th reason I'm so fond o' cookin is that me mother was a baker in Halas? Makes more sense now, eh? Alright, now 'tis yer turn.&quot; She looks expectantly at the others in the room. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=20371A><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ullylewen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Llylewen</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elder</span><br>  Posts: 305<br> <font color=#660000>(8/21/02 12:18:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fcircleofsistersfrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=261.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Tidbits of Trivia   ((open to everyone))</span><hr size=1> Llylewen muttered something nasty under her breath as she dropped her cards on the table.  &quot;A getting to know you game, eh?&quot;  She propped her head up in her palm.  &quot;Ok, I'm game.  Let's see.&quot;  She searched through her memory.  &quot;Well, I bet you didn't know I was actually raised in Freeport, away from all the other elves.  Some might say that's why I lack some of their personality characteristics.&quot;  She smirked and looked at Nullo. <p><p><font face="Calisto MT"><img border="0" src="http://www.hyperjump.net/lunap2000/llylewen2.jpg" align="left" width="104" height="104"></font><font face="Invitation" size="4">Llylewen
